LINE.Text: GLOBAL LNG MARKETS BRACE FOR UNPRECEDENTED SHOCK IN 2020 ON COVID-19
The spread of coronavirus across the world has generated an unprecedented global health and economic crisis, and presented the LNG industry with a demand shock like no other in its history.
